<p class="">I have often heard the expression "unfair competition" used in this Debate. The hon. and gallant Gentleman has used it now, as one of his main objections to the Bill. Would <span id="1434" class="column-number" data-column-number="1434"></span> he explain exactly what he means by "unfair competition"?.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
