<p class="">It depends what the hon. Member means by "a good time."</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2db9bd06-2f1d-4d96-a5e8-edfbe0e67078" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
