        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-78b6d882-f4db-4d02-aea1-a28d7de20f51">
                Mr. Fraser
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-78b6d882-f4db-4d02-aea1-a28d7de20f51" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-02-10/debates/ef376344-3876-409c-af24-c18cb6814a35/CivicRestaurantsBill#contribution-78b6d882-f4db-4d02-aea1-a28d7de20f51">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What I mean by "a good time" is that normally the restaurants should serve two purposes: the purpose of pleasure, and the purposes of necessity—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-78b6d882-f4db-4d02-aea1-a28d7de20f51" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-02-10/debates/ef376344-3876-409c-af24-c18cb6814a35/CivicRestaurantsBill#contribution-78b6d882-f4db-4d02-aea1-a28d7de20f51">
