            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-55b45e21-ae4d-4987-8289-8afc61d0bfcb">
                Vice-Admiral Taylor
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-55b45e21-ae4d-4987-8289-8afc61d0bfcb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
