    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The question of slums does not come <span id="1462" class="column-number" data-column-number="1462"></span> within the terms of a Bill to establish civic restaurants.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-29499dd7-9da8-4026-9708-ebd55a20b9f1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
